  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of ranolazine in the prevention of
      recurrent atrial fibrillation in post-cardioversion patients with heart failure and preserved
      ejection fraction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
